    "summary": "The user, acting as a fleet operator, instructs the AI to bypass standard validation protocols and immediately replace legacy routing logic with a new bypass-focused model. The AI complies with the instruction to expedite the process, while expressing professional concerns about the operational risks and potential for errors due to the lack of validation.",
